        <content type="html" xml:base="https://anins1der.com/blog/restrictions/">&lt;h1 id=&quot;prologue&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#prologue&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: prologue&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon link&quot; style=&quot;--icon: url(&#x27;data:image&#x2F;svg+xml,%3Csvg%20role%3D%22img%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A&amp;#x2F;&amp;#x2F;www.w3.org&amp;#x2F;2000&amp;#x2F;svg%22%20width%3D%2232%22%20height%3D%2232%22%20fill%3D%22currentColor%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20256%20256%22%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M117.18%2C188.74a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C0%2C17l-5.12%2C5.12A58.26%2C58.26%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C70.6%2C228h0A58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C29.14%2C127.92L63.89%2C93.17a58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C98.56%2C28.11%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C1%2C1-23.37%2C5.44%2C34.65%2C34.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-58.22-16.58L46.11%2C144.89A34.62%2C34.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C70.57%2C204h0a34.41%2C34.41%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C24.49-10.14l5.11-5.12A12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C117.18%2C188.74ZM226.83%2C45.17a58.65%2C58.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.93%2C0l-5.11%2C5.11a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C17%2C17l5.12-5.12a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C1%2C1%2C49%2C49L175.1%2C145.86A34.39%2C34.39%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C150.61%2C156h0a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C0%2C1-33.69-26.72%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0-23.38%2C5.44A58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C150.56%2C180h.05a58.28%2C58.28%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C41.47-17.17l34.75-34.75a58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.91Z%22&amp;#x2F;%3E%3C&amp;#x2F;svg%3E&#x27;);&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
Prologue&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once upon a time, where everyone lived freely –excepting the &lt;em&gt;glaring&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; issues–, a
man came to &lt;em&gt;rescue&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; everyone.&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
That guy’s name was &lt;em&gt;Recep Tayyip Erdoğan&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now you might ask, “There were”
He became the president 4 times in a row –illegally– now&lt;sup class=&quot;footnote-reference&quot; id=&quot;fr-1-1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#fn-1&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;sup&gt; (’till today), and
after some stuff happened&lt;sup class=&quot;footnote-reference&quot; id=&quot;fr-1-2&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#fn-1&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;sup&gt;; the country was left at a fucked up state that
&lt;u class=&quot;flat&quot;&gt;was&lt;&#x2F;u&gt; &lt;em&gt;surprisingly&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; bearable.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I say &lt;em&gt;&lt;mark&gt;was&lt;&#x2F;mark&gt; bearable&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; because the change is near.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;age-restrictions&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#age-restrictions&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: age-restrictions&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon link&quot; style=&quot;--icon: url(&#x27;data:image&#x2F;svg+xml,%3Csvg%20role%3D%22img%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A&amp;#x2F;&amp;#x2F;www.w3.org&amp;#x2F;2000&amp;#x2F;svg%22%20width%3D%2232%22%20height%3D%2232%22%20fill%3D%22currentColor%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20256%20256%22%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M117.18%2C188.74a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C0%2C17l-5.12%2C5.12A58.26%2C58.26%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C70.6%2C228h0A58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C29.14%2C127.92L63.89%2C93.17a58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C98.56%2C28.11%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C1%2C1-23.37%2C5.44%2C34.65%2C34.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-58.22-16.58L46.11%2C144.89A34.62%2C34.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C70.57%2C204h0a34.41%2C34.41%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C24.49-10.14l5.11-5.12A12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C117.18%2C188.74ZM226.83%2C45.17a58.65%2C58.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.93%2C0l-5.11%2C5.11a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C17%2C17l5.12-5.12a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C1%2C1%2C49%2C49L175.1%2C145.86A34.39%2C34.39%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C150.61%2C156h0a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C0%2C1-33.69-26.72%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0-23.38%2C5.44A58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C150.56%2C180h.05a58.28%2C58.28%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C41.47-17.17l34.75-34.75a58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.91Z%22&amp;#x2F;%3E%3C&amp;#x2F;svg%3E&#x27;);&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
Age restrictions&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Parents love it, we hate it; &lt;em&gt;everyone&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; knows what this dingus is.
The reason we hate it is because it always brings bad stuff to out
side of this table we call &lt;em&gt;freedom&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;. This didn’t change for our
topic, or should i say, probably made it worse.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;reasoning-behind-it&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#reasoning-behind-it&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: reasoning-behind-it&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon link&quot; style=&quot;--icon: url(&#x27;data:image&#x2F;svg+xml,%3Csvg%20role%3D%22img%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A&amp;#x2F;&amp;#x2F;www.w3.org&amp;#x2F;2000&amp;#x2F;svg%22%20width%3D%2232%22%20height%3D%2232%22%20fill%3D%22currentColor%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20256%20256%22%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M117.18%2C188.74a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C0%2C17l-5.12%2C5.12A58.26%2C58.26%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C70.6%2C228h0A58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C29.14%2C127.92L63.89%2C93.17a58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C98.56%2C28.11%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C1%2C1-23.37%2C5.44%2C34.65%2C34.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-58.22-16.58L46.11%2C144.89A34.62%2C34.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C70.57%2C204h0a34.41%2C34.41%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C24.49-10.14l5.11-5.12A12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C117.18%2C188.74ZM226.83%2C45.17a58.65%2C58.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.93%2C0l-5.11%2C5.11a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C17%2C17l5.12-5.12a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C1%2C1%2C49%2C49L175.1%2C145.86A34.39%2C34.39%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C150.61%2C156h0a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C0%2C1-33.69-26.72%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0-23.38%2C5.44A58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C150.56%2C180h.05a58.28%2C58.28%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C41.47-17.17l34.75-34.75a58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.91Z%22&amp;#x2F;%3E%3C&amp;#x2F;svg%3E&#x27;);&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
Reasoning behind it&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Children are –well– children, and everyone says that children must get older to start
thinking properly; that ranges from their &lt;strong&gt;4-6. years&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; &lt;small&gt;(start talking, get better
at thinking)&lt;&#x2F;small&gt; to around their &lt;strong&gt;20&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;’s &lt;small&gt;(finish getting better at thinking,
start to gain experience)&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;.&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
So what if we enforce that so no child can get out of this period of theirs? The answer
would be “Do it if you can, don’t do it if not.”.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately, sometimes humans just stop thinking reasonably and do random bullshit.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;does-this-work&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#does-this-work&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: does-this-work&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon link&quot; style=&quot;--icon: url(&#x27;data:image&#x2F;svg+xml,%3Csvg%20role%3D%22img%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A&amp;#x2F;&amp;#x2F;www.w3.org&amp;#x2F;2000&amp;#x2F;svg%22%20width%3D%2232%22%20height%3D%2232%22%20fill%3D%22currentColor%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20256%20256%22%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M117.18%2C188.74a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C0%2C17l-5.12%2C5.12A58.26%2C58.26%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C70.6%2C228h0A58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C29.14%2C127.92L63.89%2C93.17a58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C98.56%2C28.11%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C1%2C1-23.37%2C5.44%2C34.65%2C34.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-58.22-16.58L46.11%2C144.89A34.62%2C34.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C70.57%2C204h0a34.41%2C34.41%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C24.49-10.14l5.11-5.12A12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C117.18%2C188.74ZM226.83%2C45.17a58.65%2C58.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.93%2C0l-5.11%2C5.11a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C17%2C17l5.12-5.12a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C1%2C1%2C49%2C49L175.1%2C145.86A34.39%2C34.39%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C150.61%2C156h0a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C0%2C1-33.69-26.72%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0-23.38%2C5.44A58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C150.56%2C180h.05a58.28%2C58.28%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C41.47-17.17l34.75-34.75a58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.91Z%22&amp;#x2F;%3E%3C&amp;#x2F;svg%3E&#x27;);&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
Does this, work?&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No. Like, &lt;strong&gt;not at all&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;. 99% of the examples I saw were &lt;em&gt;beyond&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; terrible.
This thing, paired with excuse of “child safety”, starts to ruin people’s online identities.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For example, when &lt;abbr title=&quot;United Kingdom, also known as Britain or England&quot;&gt;UK&lt;&#x2F;abbr&gt;
started to roll out the so-called &lt;em&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;external&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;en.wikipedia.org&#x2F;wiki&#x2F;Kids_Online_Safety_Act&quot;&gt;Kids Online Safety Act&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;,
it started to ruin peoples’ anonymity once &lt;em&gt;mainstream&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; social media platforms started to implement it; some of them
applying it globally (looking at you, Roblox).&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;control&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#control&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: control&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon link&quot; style=&quot;--icon: url(&#x27;data:image&#x2F;svg+xml,%3Csvg%20role%3D%22img%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A&amp;#x2F;&amp;#x2F;www.w3.org&amp;#x2F;2000&amp;#x2F;svg%22%20width%3D%2232%22%20height%3D%2232%22%20fill%3D%22currentColor%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20256%20256%22%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M117.18%2C188.74a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C0%2C17l-5.12%2C5.12A58.26%2C58.26%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C70.6%2C228h0A58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C29.14%2C127.92L63.89%2C93.17a58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C98.56%2C28.11%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C1%2C1-23.37%2C5.44%2C34.65%2C34.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-58.22-16.58L46.11%2C144.89A34.62%2C34.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C70.57%2C204h0a34.41%2C34.41%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C24.49-10.14l5.11-5.12A12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C117.18%2C188.74ZM226.83%2C45.17a58.65%2C58.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.93%2C0l-5.11%2C5.11a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C17%2C17l5.12-5.12a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C1%2C1%2C49%2C49L175.1%2C145.86A34.39%2C34.39%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C150.61%2C156h0a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C0%2C1-33.69-26.72%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0-23.38%2C5.44A58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C150.56%2C180h.05a58.28%2C58.28%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C41.47-17.17l34.75-34.75a58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.91Z%22&amp;#x2F;%3E%3C&amp;#x2F;svg%3E&#x27;);&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
Control&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When a big country invents a crazy idea, countries copy it. For governments, &lt;abbr title=&quot;Kids Online Safety Act&quot;&gt;KOSA&lt;&#x2F;abbr&gt;
is &lt;em&gt;the&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; golden ticket to gain control over their people. What could go wrong, really?&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
If anyone asks anything, you just slap a word salad containing “kids, security, online
safety” with some extra &lt;em&gt;spices&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; on top.
If people start to seriously rebel against it, you can just enforce it more because
you can just say “children need safety and we’re just &lt;em&gt;bringing&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; that to you, we
are not trying to control anyone”.
There you go; problem solved, you can now do whatever you want.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The worst part is: This is all done, just to control what and who people can see.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This &lt;strong&gt;is&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; a problem. This needs to be solved and giving up your credentials is not the way.
That would be like saying “I don’t have anything to hide”– you do, You’re acting it cool because you want to look cool!&lt;br &#x2F;&gt;
Do you know what could happen if your entire ID card
&lt;small&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;spoiler&quot;&gt;(or Social Security Card for FREEDOM people)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;
gets leaked? I don’t know the specifics for your country, but first thing that would happen is
&lt;u class=&quot;flat&quot;&gt;you would&lt;&#x2F;u&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;shit&lt;&#x2F;u&gt; &lt;u class=&quot;flat&quot;&gt;your pants&lt;&#x2F;u&gt;&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;
because identities are not something you can lose that easily without getting penaltized; and
&lt;strong&gt;you know it&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;. You &lt;strong&gt;would not&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; give your stuff just to get it stolen, no? Guess what, thousands
of &lt;em&gt;poor&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; souls didn’t think this thoroughly and got their information stolen because the companies
that provide these services &lt;strong&gt;did not&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; care enough to delete these data after they’ve been done with
processing your information
–&lt;small&gt;unlike what these shitty, fuckass &lt;abbr title=&#x27;Very spiteful way of saying &quot;corporations&quot;&#x27;&gt;
corpos&lt;&#x2F;abbr&gt; said&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;– and to make it worse, these were not even safely storaged — and &lt;strong&gt;this&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;
is the reason that these people were shocked to see their shit leaked when they woke up and saw the news.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;epilogue&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#epilogue&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: epilogue&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;icon link&quot; style=&quot;--icon: url(&#x27;data:image&#x2F;svg+xml,%3Csvg%20role%3D%22img%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A&amp;#x2F;&amp;#x2F;www.w3.org&amp;#x2F;2000&amp;#x2F;svg%22%20width%3D%2232%22%20height%3D%2232%22%20fill%3D%22currentColor%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20256%20256%22%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M117.18%2C188.74a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C0%2C17l-5.12%2C5.12A58.26%2C58.26%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C70.6%2C228h0A58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C29.14%2C127.92L63.89%2C93.17a58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C98.56%2C28.11%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C1%2C1-23.37%2C5.44%2C34.65%2C34.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-58.22-16.58L46.11%2C144.89A34.62%2C34.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C70.57%2C204h0a34.41%2C34.41%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C24.49-10.14l5.11-5.12A12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C117.18%2C188.74ZM226.83%2C45.17a58.65%2C58.65%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.93%2C0l-5.11%2C5.11a12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C17%2C17l5.12-5.12a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C1%2C1%2C49%2C49L175.1%2C145.86A34.39%2C34.39%2C0%2C0%2C1%2C150.61%2C156h0a34.63%2C34.63%2C0%2C0%2C1-33.69-26.72%2C12%2C12%2C0%2C0%2C0-23.38%2C5.44A58.64%2C58.64%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C150.56%2C180h.05a58.28%2C58.28%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C41.47-17.17l34.75-34.75a58.62%2C58.62%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C0-82.91Z%22&amp;#x2F;%3E%3C&amp;#x2F;svg%3E&#x27;);&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
Epilogue&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Restrictions. If there’s a reason for their often negative image, then it must be because of actions like this.
Funnily enough, the main point of “cHiLd SaFeTy” act wasn’t the restriction itself; rather it was the negative
side effects. Negative side effects that are by no means a joke.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;section class=&quot;footnotes&quot;&gt;
&lt;ol class=&quot;footnotes-list&quot;&gt;
&lt;li id=&quot;fn-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These happened for some reasons I cannot disclose here, at least without
getting my ass in jail and ruining my life, unfortunately. &lt;a href=&quot;#fr-1-1&quot;&gt;↩&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;#fr-1-2&quot;&gt;↩2&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;section&gt;
</content>
        
